metadata.name: Serenity
metadata.description:
This is the 1st 1/1st NFT in a collection of 4 photographs.
Size: 2656 x 3984 px
The big city is always about speed.
This city never sleeps. People are always running and rushing.
Someone is late for work again, someone is in a traffic jam taking a child to school, and someone is running to a meeting. Everyone wants to reach their goals as quickly as possible. But sometimes it's important to slow down and remember who you are.
Every woman wants to feel like a little princess. To remember their true desires and dreams. After all, so often we get someone else's imposed goals. In a huge city, it's easy to get lost in the abundance of choices and opportunities. It's important to choose your path, it's important to choose YOU.
And do not forget that you are still the same little princess, who knows how to listen and hear HIM and enjoy the moment.
These photos helped me to see another side of Myself and to remember that I am still a little princess.
